-- Egypt's Amer Group posts 87 pct drop in Q1 profit
-- By Stephen Kalin
-- Thu May 08, 2014 03:53AM EDT
-- None



CAIRO, May 8 (Reuters) - Egypt real estate company Amer Group's <AMER.CA> first-quarter net profit fell 87 percent to 2.026 million Egyptian pounds ($288,200), the company said in a statement sent to the stock exchange on Thursday.

Net profit was 15.352 million pounds in the same period a year earlier.